'''高地與群島大學'''（{{lang-en|University of the Highlands and Islands}}，{{lang-gd|Oilthigh na Gàidhealtachd agus nan Eilean}}）是一座在[[蘇格蘭|蘇格蘭]][[高地和群島|高地和群島]]地區由13所研究機構共同組建的[[聯合學校|聯合學校]]。行政辦公室在[[印威內斯|印威內斯]]。

==歷史==
高地與群島大學是蘇格蘭最新的大學，<ref name=FactsFigures>{{cite web|title=Facts and figures|url=http://www.uhi.ac.uk/en/about-uhi/facts-and-figures|publisher=The University of the Highlands and Islands|accessdate=6 January 2013|archive-date=2021-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210420111442/https://www.uhi.ac.uk/en/about-uhi/facts-and-figures/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 下共13個學院和研究機構。

2001年4月，[[蘇格蘭議會|蘇格蘭議會]]授予該大學高等教育機構之地位，現提供大學級課程。2008年以前其文憑由[[公開大學|公開大學]]、[[斯特拉斯克萊德大學|斯特拉斯克萊德大學]]和[[阿伯丁大學|阿伯丁大學]]提供，當年高地與群島大學獲得[[英國樞密院|英國樞密院]]授予的學位頒發許可。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.highland.gov.uk/yourcouncil/news/newsreleases/2008/June/2008-06-26-01.htm |title=''UHI is awarded taught degree awarding powers'', news release 26 June 2008, Highland Council website, accessed 20 March 2009 |publisher=Highland.gov.uk |date=2008-06-26 |accessdate=2011-02-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110728050606/http://www.highland.gov.uk/yourcouncil/news/newsreleases/2008/June/2008-06-26-01.htm |archivedate=2011-07-28}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.uhi.ac.uk/home/about-uhi/publications/compass-news/ecompass/issue-6-june-2008/taught-degree-awarding-powers-for-uhi |title=University of the Highlands and Islands |publisher=UHI |date= |accessdate=2011-02-02 }}{{dead link|date=2018年5月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.qaa.ac.uk/reviews/dap/briefGuideDAP.asp |title=''A brief guide to QAA's involvement in degree-awarding powers and university title'', Quality Assurance Agency for Higher Education (QAA) website, accessed 20 March 2009 |publisher=QAA |date=2004-09-01 |accessdate=2011-02-02 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100715141505/http://www.qaa.ac.uk/reviews/dap/briefGuideDAP.asp |archivedate=2010-07-15}}</ref> 2011年2月獲得大學地位，更現名。
